{
  "chapter": 103,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与善柔换上鹿皮防水衣，携铜管等装备，借送赵雅之机离开行馆。途中遇田单车队，乌果假扮董匡应对得体。两人潜入水道，经侯府荷花池，利用铜管在水下换气，克服恶犬巡逻的阻碍，辗转抵达碧桃园。项少龙灵机一动用布帛包扎铜管增加储气量，两人终于成功潜至卧客轩。轩内发现赵穆的大铁箱，正欲开锁时守卫涌入，两人紧急攀上横梁躲避。赵穆带田单、李园到来，欲展示效忠书。本章善柔展现独立坚强个性，与项少龙感情进一步深化。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔姊不到我这里来吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "雅儿想好了吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这样好吗？你走后人家待一段时间才溜往某处会你。唉！若教人不知你的安危而离开，只是担心就可担心死赵雅了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "假若你王兄突然逝世，权力落到晶王后手内，她肯放过你吗？那时我回到咸阳，鞭长莫及，怎样助你呢！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她阵脚未稳，凭什么来对付我，况且她始终是韩人，若刚上场就拿我们王族的人开刀，王公大臣岂会让她得逞，那时我若要走，她欢迎还来不及哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "唉！少龙！人家害怕的是别的事啊！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "赵雅你说话可否大声点。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "雅儿怕什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "怕别的人不原谅人家嘛！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "回咸阳后我会为你做一番功夫，廷芳和倩公主是胸无城府的人，不会记恨，其他人更不用担心，这叫将功赎罪啊！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "准备！经过侯王府。噢！真精彩，田单的车队对头开来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_dong_kuang",
      "text": "董将军辛苦了，我们这些闲人去饮酒作乐，你们却日忙夜忙，不过人的体力终有限度，董将军可勿忙坏了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_kuang",
      "speaker_name": "乌果（扮董匡）",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "我这人天生粗贱，愈忙愈精神，谢田相关心了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人这几天容光焕发，神采飞扬，可愿告知田某其中妙诀？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "赵雅可不依哩！田相在笑人家。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凡有池塘的府第，必有入水口和出水口，这是我善柔的大秘密，上趟我便是由这里潜往那奸贼府内的大池塘里的，若幸运的话，说不定我们还可直通至碧桃园那条人工河去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这里离开侯府足有百丈之遥，如何换气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真蠢！人家可以进去，自然有换气的方法，那枝铜管难道是白给你的吗？除非刚下完大雨，否则河水和入府的大渠顶间总有寸许空隙，只要把铜管一端啣在口中，另一端伸出水面，不是可解决问题吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这是奖励！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "糟了！有这些畜牲在岸上，我们唯有靠水道摸到那里去。若卧客轩也放了两头恶犬在那里，我们只好回家睡觉。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "找到哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我游了足有两丈，前边的方向似乎没有问题，但这里离碧桃园最少数百步的距离，我们怎能一口气游到那么远的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "由这里到碧桃园还有一个池塘，我看水道应先通到那个池塘去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "即使池塘刚在正中处，离这里也有百多步的距离，我们仍是到不了那处去的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我有办法了，只要我们把铜管的一端包扎着，另一端用手按紧，管内的余气可足够我们换上两、三次气，不是可潜到那边去吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这人原来并不大蠢，但用什么东西包扎管口？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我的皮衣里只有一条短裤，你里面有穿东西吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这好色鬼，噢！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "会漏气吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "有三层布包裹着，湿透后纵或会漏出少许空气，但那时我们早由那边出口钻出去了。来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天更不妙，我们最多只游过百步的距离，由这里到碧桃园那条人工小河，少说还有两百步以上的距离，远近尚不能肯定，铜管的空气怎够用？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你给我亲个嘴，我便可想到办法。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若是骗我，便宰了你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快说！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "我们把头罩割下来，用布条在管口扎紧，不是可多几口气吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不愧是我善柔的第一个男人，不过今趟由我负责，人家不信你的手工。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "什么第一个男人，你大小姐还会有第二、第三个男人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你们男人可以有很多女人，为何女人不可以亦有很多男人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "那谁还敢娶你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁要嫁人呢？天下这么大，若干掉赵穆、田单，我便四处浪荡，或者有天累了，就来找你吧！那时你要不要人家也没打紧。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你看！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这种锁我还是第一次见到，怎打开它呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "让我这开锁宗师来看看吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上横梁！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "府卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点灯！打开窗子，侯爷和客人快到哩！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "抱紧我！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都给本侯出去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 103,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    }
  ],
